@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
actor Doctor
participant "Doctor UI" as UI
participant "Drug Library" as DrugLib
participant "Logical System" as LogicSys
participant "Audit Logger" as Logger
database "System DB" as DB

Doctor -> UI : Login (Doctor Credentials)
UI -> Auth : Authenticate
Auth --> UI : Success (Role: Doctor)

Doctor -> UI : Access Drug Library
UI -> DrugLib : Fetch All Drugs
DrugLib -> DB : Query Drugs
DB --> UI : Display List

Doctor -> UI : Edit Safety Limits (Hard Limit Ceiling)
UI -> DrugLib : Update Drug Parameters
DrugLib -> Logger : Log Immutable: "Hard Limit Changed for [Drug]"
DrugLib -> DB : Commit Changes
DB --> UI : Updated
UI --> Doctor : Confirmation Message

== Analytics & Reporting ==
Doctor -> UI : Request Clinical Analytics [F-D-05]
UI -> LogicSys : Generate Report (Last 30 Days)
LogicSys -> Logger : Fetch Audit History
Logger --> LogicSys : Data Points
LogicSys -> LogicSys : Format PDF/CSV
UI -> Doctor : Display Report & Provide Export Link
Doctor -> UI : Export to PDF
UI --> Doctor : Download Triggered
@enduml